divs: Sighting DetailsI was turning right into the parking lot of 429 S Evergreen Ave when I just happened to look up and noticed two airplanes in the air over the building to the west. I then noticed the white light moving in an intercept course with the lower plane. At first I thought that the object was a star before I realized it was moving. I thought it was strange that they looked to be so close, much less going to intersect. The plane was moving in a straight westernly direction and as the white light almost touched it, the white light seemed to accelerate and make a hook shaped maneuver away from the plane. The white light was still moving when I lost sight of the plane and white light as they were blocked from view by the building. I parked my car and got out, looking back in the direction that they were, but I could no longer see the plane or the white light.
